    "en": {
      "name": "Xyz Unbreakable Barrier",
      "effect": "When a Spell/Trap Card, or monster effect, is activated and you control an Xyz Monster: Negate the activation, then you can detach 2 materials from a monster(s) you control, then destroy 1 card on the field. You can banish this card from your GY, then target 1 Xyz Monster you control; attach 1 LIGHT \"Utopia\" or \"Utopic\" Xyz Monster from your GY to it as material. You can only use each effect of \"Xyz Unbreakable Barrier\" once per turn.",
      "official": false
    },
